---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Courses — BitGuru"
  description="Master the crypto markets with BitGuru's comprehensive curriculum — from blockchain fundamentals to professional technical analysis."
>
  <div class="pt-32 pb-24 space-y-32">

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high text-primary-fixed-dim text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide border border-outline-variant/20 uppercase">Advanced Curriculum</span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-display font-extrabold tracking-tight text-on-background leading-tight">
          Master the <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary-container">Crypto Markets</span> like a Guru.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
          A comprehensive journey from blockchain fundamentals to professional technical analysis. Curated for those who demand precision in the world of decentralized finance.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="#enroll" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary-container text-on-primary-fixed px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform">
            Enroll in Masterclass
          </a>
          <a href="#curriculum" class="bg-surface-container-highest text-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-surface-bright transition-colors">
            View Curriculum
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative group">
        <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-tr from-primary/20 to-secondary-fixed-dim/20 blur-3xl opacity-50"></div>
        <div class="relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden aspect-video shadow-2xl border border-outline-variant/10">
          <img
            alt="Crypto Trading Interface"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDEpUKXMJEcnqnyUvgFgS7a4w759ZuNK7Xkw-XNli5KhC2KSJfty9o-4M6-v055D7mo2rfPOj0FsNXwvOnqAklrrT8Elzc9wXDjV_rXKq2S_PTxji626tFY8shiYuEOewwBexHENEwZaEhZrXUlEwOSRlHW3XpokjdAX7DQhyN_8Zr7PuPu2kKKooMXJLGYr7C4o-VG5t0WDiLOdVADndGPPC69LQYoMS2eeW48Q59c-gjOtd7_0bwKxXsY-nZXBHaHkr-S2Gd8Xg"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface-dim via-transparent to-transparent opacity-60"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Value Prop: What You'll Learn -->
    <section class="bg-surface-container-low py-24">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-on-background tracking-tight">What You'll Learn</h2>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto">From your first wallet to professional-grade algorithmic patterns.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Phase 1 -->
          <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant/10 hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <!-- foundation icon -->
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M160-120v-80h640v80H160Zm80-120v-320h80v320h-80Zm160 0v-320h80v320h-80Zm160 0v-320h80v320h-80Zm160 0v-320h80v320h-80ZM80-560v-80l400-200 400 200v80H80Z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-on-background mb-3">Beginner Fundamentals</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Master blockchain mechanics, wallet security, and the psychology of decentralization.</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Phase 2 -->
          <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant/10 hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary-container/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-primary-container group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <!-- analytics icon -->
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M280-280h80v-200h-80v200Zm160 0h80v-400h-80v400Zm160 0h80v-120h-80v120ZM200-120q-33 0-56.5-23.5T120-200v-560q0-33 23.5-56.5T200-840h560q33 0 56.5 23.5T840-760v560q0 33-23.5 56.5T760-120H200Zm0-80h560v-560H200v560Zm0-560v560-560Z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-on-background mb-3">Technical Mastery</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Learn candlestick patterns, RSI, Fibonacci levels, and liquidity zone identification.</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Phase 3 -->
          <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant/10 hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-secondary-fixed-dim/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-secondary-fixed-dim group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <!-- auto_graph icon -->
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="m136-240-56-56 296-298 160 160 208-240 56 56-264 302-160-160-240 236Zm584 80-56-84-84 56 56-84-84-56 84-56-56-84 84 56 56-84 56 84 84-56-56 84 84 56-84 56 56 84Z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-on-background mb-3">Advanced Strategy</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Risk management frameworks, algorithmic backtesting, and DeFi yield farming tactics.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Course Breakdown -->
    <section id="curriculum" class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16">
        <div class="lg:w-1/3">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-on-background sticky top-32 leading-tight">Comprehensive<br/>Module Breakdown</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:w-2/3 space-y-6">
          <!-- Module 1 -->
          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-high border-l-4 border-primary shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-primary-fixed font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">Module 01</span>
              <span class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">4 Lessons • 2h 15m</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-on-background">Introduction to Blockchain &amp; Ecosystems</h4>
            <p class="mt-2 text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Understanding L1 vs L2, consensus mechanisms, and the future of Ethereum.</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Module 2 -->
          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-high border-l-4 border-primary/40 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-primary-fixed font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">Module 02</span>
              <span class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">8 Lessons • 5h 30m</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-on-background">Technical Analysis Deep Dive</h4>
            <p class="mt-2 text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Identifying trends, volume profile, and order block analysis.</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Module 3 -->
          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-high border-l-4 border-primary/20 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-primary-fixed font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">Module 03</span>
              <span class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">6 Lessons • 4h 00m</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-on-background">Risk Management &amp; Execution</h4>
            <p class="mt-2 text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Position sizing, emotional control, and setting up your trading station.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Bonus Features -->
    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Community -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-surface-container-high border border-outline-variant/10 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10">
          <!-- groups icon -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M0-240v-63q0-43 44-70t116-27q13 0 25 .5t23 2.5q-14 21-21 44t-7 46v67H0Zm240 0v-67q0-32 17.5-58.5T307-410q32-20 76.5-30t96.5-10q53 0 97.5 10t76.5 30q32 20 49 46.5t17 58.5v67H240Zm540 0v-67q0-24-6.5-46.5T754-397q11-2 22.5-2.5t23.5-.5q72 0 116 26.5t44 70.5v63H780Zm-480-80h360v-6q0-9-4.5-18T645-361q-20-14-57.5-23.5T480-394q-53 0-90 9.5T333-361q-9 7-13.5 16t-4.5 18v6ZM160-440q-33 0-56.5-23.5T80-520q0-34 23.5-57t56.5-23q34 0 57 23t23 57q0 33-23 56.5T160-440Zm640 0q-33 0-56.5-23.5T720-520q0-34 23.5-57t56.5-23q34 0 57 23t23 57q0 33-23 56.5T800-440Zm-320-40q-50 0-85-35t-35-85q0-51 35-85.5t85-34.5q51 0 85.5 34.5T600-600q0 50-34.5 85T480-480Zm0-80q17 0 28.5-11.5T520-600q0-17-11.5-28.5T480-640q-17 0-28.5 11.5T440-600q0 17 11.5 28.5T480-560Zm0 240Zm0-280Z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold mb-2">Exclusive Community</h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Join the 'Alpha Inner Circle' for real-time trade discussions and support.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Mentorship -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-surface-container-high border border-outline-variant/10 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10">
          <!-- school icon -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M480-120 200-272v-240L40-600l440-240 440 240v320h-80v-276l-80 44v240L480-120Zm0-332 274-148-274-148-274 148 274 148Zm0 220 200-108v-151L480-360 280-471v151l200 108Zm0-220Zm0 90Zm0 0Z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold mb-2">1-on-1 Mentorship</h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Monthly private sessions with senior analysts to review your portfolio.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Insights -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-surface-container-high border border-outline-variant/10 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10">
          <!-- insights icon -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M480-80q-83 0-141.5-58.5T280-280q0-48 18.5-89.5T352-446l-72-72 56-56 80 80q26-10 53.5-15t50.5-5q27 0 54 5t51 15l80-80 56 56-72 72q35 37 53.5 78.5T760-280q0 83-58.5 141.5T480-80Zm0-80q50 0 85-35t35-85q0-50-35-85t-85-35q-50 0-85 35t-35 85q0 50 35 85t85 35Zm-40-80h80v-80h-80v80Zm0-120h80v-80h-80v80ZM240-560q-50 0-85-35t-35-85q0-50 35-85t85-35q50 0 85 35t35 85q0 50-35 85t-85 35Zm480 0q-50 0-85-35t-35-85q0-50 35-85t85-35q50 0 85 35t35 85q0 50-35 85t-85 35Z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold mb-2">Weekly Market Insights</h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Exclusive macro reports delivered to your inbox every Sunday morning.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pricing Section -->
    <section id="enroll" class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8">
      <div class="relative p-[1px] rounded-[2rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary-fixed/50 to-primary-container/50 shadow-2xl shadow-secondary-fixed-dim/10">
        <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-[2rem] p-12 text-center">
          <span class="text-secondary-fixed-dim font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs">Premium Access</span>
          <h2 class="text-5xl font-display font-black text-on-background mt-4 mb-2">The Guru Pathway</h2>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-8">
            <span class="text-on-surface-variant line-through text-2xl">$1,499</span>
            <span class="text-5xl font-display font-extrabold text-on-background">$899</span>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-4 text-left max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <!-- check_circle filled -->
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" fill="currentColor" class="text-secondary-fixed-dim flex-shrink-0">
                <path d="m424-296 282-282-56-56-226 226-114-114-56 56 170 170Zm56 216q-83 0-156-31.5T197-197q-54-54-85.5-127T80-480q0-83 31.5-156T197-763q54-54 127-85.5T480-880q83 0 156 31.5T763-763q54 54 85.5 127T880-480q0 83-31.5 156T763-197q-54 54-127 85.5T480-80Z"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-on-surface">Lifetime Course Access</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" fill="currentColor" class="text-secondary-fixed-dim flex-shrink-0">
                <path d="m424-296 282-282-56-56-226 226-114-114-56 56 170 170Zm56 216q-83 0-156-31.5T197-197q-54-54-85.5-127T80-480q0-83 31.5-156T197-763q54-54 127-85.5T480-880q83 0 156 31.5T763-763q54 54 85.5 127T880-480q0 83-31.5 156T763-197q-54 54-127 85.5T480-80Z"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-on-surface">Private Discord Access</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" fill="currentColor" class="text-secondary-fixed-dim flex-shrink-0">
                <path d="m424-296 282-282-56-56-226 226-114-114-56 56 170 170Zm56 216q-83 0-156-31.5T197-197q-54-54-85.5-127T80-480q0-83 31.5-156T197-763q54-54 127-85.5T480-880q83 0 156 31.5T763-763q54 54 85.5 127T880-480q0 83-31.5 156T763-197q-54 54-127 85.5T480-80Z"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-on-surface">Weekly Live Q&amp;As</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" fill="currentColor" class="text-secondary-fixed-dim flex-shrink-0">
                <path d="m424-296 282-282-56-56-226 226-114-114-56 56 170 170Zm56 216q-83 0-156-31.5T197-197q-54-54-85.5-127T80-480q0-83 31.5-156T197-763q54-54 127-85.5T480-880q83 0 156 31.5T763-763q54 54 85.5 127T880-480q0 83-31.5 156T763-197q-54 54-127 85.5T480-80Z"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-on-surface">Trading Tool Templates</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="/checkout" class="block w-full max-w-md mx-auto bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary-fixed-dim to-secondary-container text-on-secondary font-black py-5 rounded-2xl text-xl hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform shadow-xl shadow-secondary-fixed/20 text-center">
            Enroll and Get Started
          </a>
          <p class="mt-6 text-on-surface-variant text-xs">Secure Checkout • No hidden fees • 14-Day Guarantee</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-on-background mb-12 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant/10">
          <h4 class="font-display font-bold text-on-background mb-2">Is this for beginners?</h4>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Absolutely. We start with the absolute basics of blockchain before scaling up to high-frequency trading concepts.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant/10">
          <h4 class="font-display font-bold text-on-background mb-2">What do I need to start?</h4>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Just a laptop and a stable internet connection. We will guide you through setting up all necessary software.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant/10">
          <h4 class="font-display font-bold text-on-background mb-2">Is there a refund policy?</h4>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">We offer a 14-day no-questions-asked refund policy if you haven't completed more than 20% of the course.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
